WEBVTT

00:11.000 --> 00:12.300
Bad!

00:14.600 --> 00:16.200
Look at you, Bud!
- I can see the mountains!

00:20.100 --> 00:21.900
I haven't felt like this ever!

00:23.600 --> 00:24.900
This is insane! (?)

